IoT</h4><div class="separator  small left  " style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 15px;background-color: #f8e100;height: 2px;width: 40px;"></div>
<p style=''>Analytics is at the core of IoT as they support the decision-making process in operations that are created in business transformation and digital business programs. Managing and storing high velocity IoT data in an efficient and timely manner requires specialized systems &amp; algorithms. With the advent of specialized Analytics cloud platforms, this is becoming a reality for Enterprise uptake.</p><a itemprop='url' class='icon_with_title_link' href='analytics-iot/' target='_self' style='color: #0095da;'>Learn More</a></div></div></div><div class="separator  transparent   " style="margin-bottom: 25px;"></div>
